OL,3,CProportion of Guernsey men reporting
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse rises
OL,6,FThe proportion of men reporting
OL,7,Fdomestic abuse is rising year on year
OL,8,Fin Guernsey.
OL,10,FFigures from Citizens Advice reveal
OL,11,F23% of victims recorded by the service
OL,12,Flast year were male - or 14 of the 62
OL,13,Fvictims identified.
OL,15,FHowever, the service still suspect
OL,16,Fthat domestic abuse of men is under-
OL,17,Freported in the island, because the
OL,18,Fproportion is still smaller than ONS
OL,19,Ffigures for England and Wales.
