OL,3,CProportion of Guernsey men reporting
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse rises
OL,6,FThe report said: "It is likely that
OL,7,Fmany people are reluctant to contact
OL,8,Fus or the Police".
OL,10,FElsewhere, it was revealed that in
OL,11,F2023 there was a significant increase
OL,12,Fin the reporting of 'hidden' abuse:
OL,13,F'Psychological', 'Coercive Control'
OL,14,Fand 'Financial Abuse' accounted for
OL,15,F63% of cases.
OL,17,FIf you need support about an issue
OL,18,Fraised in one of ITV Channel's
OL,19,Fstories, there are local organisations
OL,20,Fwho can help.
